HEADWORD: Non sequitur
<hw>Non seq"ui*tur</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L., it does not
follow.]</ety> <fld>(Logic)</fld> <def>An inference which does not
follow from the premises.</def>⟦br⟧
